alaMldHelperAddress.name: alaMldHelperAddress
alaMldHelperAddress.description: The configured IPv6 helper address. When an MLD report or leave is received by the device it will remove the IP header and regenerate a new IP header with a destination IP address specified. Use :: to no longer help an MLD report to an remote address. Must be set at the same time as alaMldHelperAddressType
